dcterms:description: A dataset containing a large ensemble of voxelized 3D microstructures with diverse morphological features, generated through convolution with various Gaussian filters, and their associated effective elastic stiffness properties estimated using finite element method simulations.
dcterms:title: 3-D microstructures and elasticity properties
